th.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 0aComing of agezCentral AmericavArt. 0aIndian artzCentral America. 0aMaya art. 0aMayasxAntiquities. 0aMayas. 0aYoung men in art. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030023017840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300230178423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300230178/original  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles